t nbc universal ms hall pioneered the creation of the company’s groundbreaking education nation platform ms hall joined nbc universal in  after acquired oxygen media she cofounded oxygen media llc in  and served as its president and chief operating officer since july  ms hall led the daytoday operations of oxygen media llc and served as the principal engineer of oxygens foundation partnerships with carseywerner llc and harpo productions inc she was also responsible for oxygen media llcs financing and major mso agreements and in  led oxygen to its first year of positive cash flow ms hall was principally responsible for the sale of oxygen to nbc universal she served as the interim chief executive officer of the weather channel interactive inc from september  to july  she played a major role in securing distribution for the womenoriented network which is in  million homes in addition she engineered oxygens foundation partnerships including carseywernermandabach harpo vulcan and financing she founded the new york law firm friedman kaplan  seiler llp where she served as a founding partner from  to  she started her legal career at debevoise and plimpton ms gersh has over  years of experience in creating strong corporate partnerships negotiating financing and other strategic relationships she has been a director of comscore inc since june   she has been an independent director of hasbro inc since july   she served as a director of martha stewart living omnimedia inc from july  to february   she served as director of xo group inc alternate name the knot inc from june   to june   ms gersh holds a ba in political science and economics from the state university of new york binghamton in  and a jd from rutgers law school in  and admitted to the new york state bar association in read full background corporate headquarters  newport avenuepawtucket rhode island united statesphone fax  board members memberships presentindependent directorhasbro incpresentdirectorcomscore inc educat